OKR Board is a perfect system for those who want to implement OKRs in their company. It allows you to set up your OKRs in only a couple of clicks, automatically tracks linked JIRA issues and tasks, and places all your performance metrics on a single Dashboard.

Features:
✔️ Custom OKR levels: Strategic, Company, Department, Group, etc.;
✔️ Custom OKR weights and types: Binary, Number, Percentile;
✔️ Custom OKR breakdown periods: Year>Quarter>Month;
✔️ Public and private Workspaces with user roles;
✔️ Automated Dashboards for reports and analytics;
✔️ Public API for data export.

OKR Board can be further powered up by installing the Confluence plugin and implementing an OKR knowledge base.

